{"word":"G554 - ἀπεκδύομαι - apekdýomai - ap-ek-doo'-om-ahee - Put off","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπεκδύομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apekdýomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ek-doo'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Put off</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உரி, களைந்து போடு"},{"paragraph":"wholly to put off from oneself"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G1562 - ἐκδύω - ekdýō - ek-doo'-o/1562\">G1562</a>; to <i>divest wholly</i> oneself, or (for oneself) <i>despoil:</i> - put off, spoil.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1416/1416\">G1416</a>, <a href=\"#/G1562/1562\">G1562</a>, <a href=\"#/G1744/1744\">G1744</a>, <a href=\"#/G1902/1902\">G1902</a>, <a href=\"#/G554/554\">G554</a>, <a href=\"#/G555/555\">G555</a>"}]}